#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationnodestatemachinetransition.rst:60
msgid ""
"**SWITCH_MODE_IMMEDIATE** = **0** --- Switch to the next state "
"immediately. The current state will end and blend into the beginning of "
"the new one."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationnodestatemachinetransition.rst:62
msgid ""
"**SWITCH_MODE_SYNC** = **1** --- Switch to the next state immediately, "
"but will seek the new state to the playback position of the old state."
msgstr ""

#: /home/bee/code/godot/godot-docs-l10n/docs/classes/class_animationnodestatemachinetransition.rst:64
msgid ""
"**SWITCH_MODE_AT_END** = **2** --- Wait for the current state playback to"
" end, then switch to the beginning of the next state animation."
msgstr ""

