"#controlling-from-code>`_). For example, if :ref:`AnimationTree.tree_root"
" <class_AnimationTree_property_tree_root>` is an "
":ref:`AnimationNodeStateMachine <class_AnimationNodeStateMachine>` and "
":ref:`advance_condition "
"<class_AnimationNodeStateMachineTransition_property_advance_condition>` "
"is set to ``\"idle\"``:"
